<i>adjective</i>: 헐렁헐렁하다 [헐렁헐렁하다], 헐렁하다 [헐렁하다], 허술하다 [허술하다], 해이하다 [해ː이하다], 어수룩하다 [어수루카다] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>헐렁헐렁하다 [헐렁헐렁하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. loose; baggy; slack</dd><br>
<dd>꼭 맞지 않고 매우 헐거운 듯한 느낌이 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>Being very loose without being fastened tight to something else.</dd><br>
<dd>2. slack; lax; rough; reckless</dd><br>
<dd>행동이 조심스럽지 않고 매우 믿음직하지 못하다.</dd><br>
<dd>One's actions being careless and extremely unreliable.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>헐렁하다 [헐렁하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. loose; baggy; slack</dd><br>
<dd>꼭 맞지 않고 헐거운 듯한 느낌이 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>Being loose without being fastened tight to something else.</dd><br>
<dd>2. slack; lax; rough; reckless</dd><br>
<dd>행동이 조심스럽지 않고 믿음직하지 못하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Acting carelessly and unreliably.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>허술하다 [허술하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. shabby; humble</dd><br>
<dd>낡고 헐어서 보잘것없다.</dd><br>
<dd>Being old and worn out, making it look worthless.</dd><br>
<dd>2. lax; slack</dd><br>
<dd>꼼꼼하지 못하고 빈틈이 있다.</dd><br>
<dd>Not meticulous, showing a loophole.</dd><br>
<dd>3. indifferent; inattentive; negligent</dd><br>
<dd>태도나 행동이 무심하고 소홀하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Looking or acting indifferent or paying little attention to something.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>해이하다 [해ː이하다]</dt><br>
<dd>slack; lax; loose</dd><br>
<dd>긴장이나 지켜야 할 규율 등이 풀려 마음이 느슨하다.</dd><br>
<dd>One's mind easing due to the release of tension or loosening of rules one is expected to follow.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>어수룩하다 [어수루카다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. naive; unsophisticated</dd><br>
<dd>말이나 행동이 순진하며 약지 않다.</dd><br>
<dd>One's way of speaking or behaving being innocent, not shrewd.</dd><br>
<dd>2. gullible; half-witted</dd><br>
<dd>아주 둔하고 어리석다.</dd><br>
<dd>Very dull and foolish.</dd><br>
<dd>3. loose; lax</dd><br>
<dd>통제가 제대로 되지 않고 매우 느슨하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Not being controlled properly and not strict.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>